# Raspberry Pi Deploy

After committing and pushing changes to `main`, deploy to the Raspberry Pi:

```bash
ssh mennano@192.168.1.60
cd agora-voice-chatbot-web
git pull origin main
docker-compose down && docker-compose up -d --build
```

## Steps

1. `git add` + `git commit` + `git push origin main`
2. SSH into Raspberry Pi: `ssh mennano@192.168.1.60`
3. Navigate to project: `cd agora-voice-chatbot-web`
4. Pull latest: `git pull origin main`
5. Rebuild containers: `docker-compose down && docker-compose up -d --build`
